text: Magdy Gheriani (born 18 February 1931) is an Egyptian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Egypt Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
